  "options": [
    {"slogan": "...", "rationale": "..."},
    ...   /* 2-3 options */
  ],
  "priority_factors_addressed": [
    {"factor_name": "...", "how_addressed": "..."},
    ...
  ]
}

== MODULE-SPECIFIC QUALITY DIRECTIVES ==
- Short, punchy, internal-tribe-y. Not market-facing.
- "Build > Talk" or "Ship the Truth" — NOT "Empowering tomorrow's leaders".
- Distinguish clearly from Tagline. If Tagline is also active in the scope, DO NOT duplicate it; this is the INTERNAL version.
